version_description: This song is in the key of Bb
Ok so I have been looking for this but all the ones I've seen sound wrong so this is.
this version has a capo, which makes the tab sound more accurate according to the song
Simple chords, even with a key change half way through when the song progresses into 'Carry On'. The capo is on 2 but can be moved depending on vocal range.
this song is in the key of E
I play this song with no capo, but you can add one if you like. it's very close to the version that they play live. :).
Here are the chords from the live version, when they performed it on the Canadian and American leg from their SLFL tour. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UJ-KN8Lt2C0.
My tab's version is different because i use special chords, it's not the same as original power chords, and the sound is better.
